LAHORE, Mar 10 (APP):Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has expressed a deep sense of sorrow over the death of Anwar Hussain Haqi, senior journalist and reporter daily Aaj News Lahore.
In a condolence message on Tuesday, he extended sympathies and condolences to the bereaved family and prayed that may Allah Almighty rest the departed soul in eternal peace.
